codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand latin grammar. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. Sicilia īnsula est. Sicilia et Sardinia ~ sunt.
